js-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ioc1665702647146.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ioc1665702647146.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ioc1665702647146.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ioc1665702647146\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      First Day of Week (\n                              FirstDayOfWeek)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Numeric value representing the day that is considered to be the first day of the week, with <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> representing Monday and <code class=\"ph codeph\">6</code> representing Sunday. Default is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">6</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__p_d103694e1_d103695e1_d103696e1\">FirstDayOfWeek<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Monday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Tuesday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Wednesday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Thursday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">4</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Friday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">5</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Saturday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">6</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ioc1665702647146__table_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sunday</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__section_kmj_j2n_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d201266e232\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__pre_hw4_k2n_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(CALENDAR) = \"FirstDayOfWeek=0\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ioc1665702647146__section_n32_l2n_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d201266e241\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svk1665702646925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svk1665702646925.html\" title=\"The umonthcalendar widget displays a month calendar to enable the user to select a date. Uniface provides a logical widget called MonthCalendar, which is mapped to umonthcalendar.\">(umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613745\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613745\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "First Day of Week ( FirstDayOfWeek) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 First Day of Week ( FirstDayOfWeek) Numeric value representing the day that is considered to be the first day of the week, with 0 representing Monday and 6 representing Sunday. Default is 6 . FirstDayOfWeek = \" Number \" Value Description 0 Monday 1 Tuesday 2 Wednesday 3 Thursday 4 Friday 5 Saturday 6 Sunday Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(CALENDAR) = \"FirstDayOfWeek=0\" Copy Applies To (umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}